                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-605" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-605" type="surname" value="LAZARUS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-605" type="given" value="SOLOMON"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18451215-289-offence-1 t18451215-name-605"></join>Solomon Lazarus</persName>; and that Mutton had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18451215-name-606" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-606" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-606" type="surname" value="LAZARUS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-606" type="given" value="SOLOMON"></interp>SOLOMON LAZARUS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a broker, and live in Bethnal-green-road. This clock-weight is mine—I lost it from the open window on Tuesday, the 9th of Dec., about seven o'clock—I had seen it safe about half-past six—I saw the prisoners pass the door about half-past six, or a quarter to seven, with some more boys—after missing the weight, I went out, and saw the prisoners about 200 yards from the shop, standing close together, but not talking—I caught hold of them both, and said, "You have got my clock-weight"—they both said they had not—I took them towards the shop, and as we went I heard something fall from Mutton—I looked down, and saw the weight sticking up in the mud—a little girl picked it up.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18451215-name-607" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-607" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-607" type="surname" value="BIVAND"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-607" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BIVAND</persName>
                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took the prisoners into custody, and told them what it was for—they said they knew nothing about it—I received the weight, and have produced it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Mutton's Defence.</hi> I was standing looking at a baker's shop when the gentleman came up and took me; I did not have the weight.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
