                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I produce a certificate of Mutton's former conviction from Clerkenwell—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted on the 15th July, on his own confession, of larceny, and confined three months and whipped</hi>)—I was pre<lb></lb>sent at the time—the prisoner is the person.</p>
